All Implemented Interfaces:
Addable<Message>, Appendable<Message>, Indexable<Message>, Prependable<Message>, Sequence<Message>, Receiver, Transmitter, NamedObject, Countable, Sized, NewInstance<BaseList<Message>>, CompressibleCollection, AsString, Listener, MessageCounter, Transceiver, Iterable<Message>, Collection<Message>, List<Message>, RandomAccess
public class ValidationIssues extends MessageList
A MessageList and MessageCounter that captures validation issues. Any message with a Message.Status worse than or equal to that of a Glitch causes isValid() to return false. In particular, capturing a Glitch or Problem makes this ValidationIssues object invalid.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
